title: Nintendo Direct Full Presentation | June 2023
description:
Tune in on June 21 at 7:00 a.m. PT for a Nintendo Direct livestream featuring roughly 40 minutes of information focused mainly on Nintendo Switch titles launching this year, including new details on Pikmin 4. We even got to see a brand new Super Mario Bros. game, Super Mario Bros. Wonder which is a 2D platformer.

title: METAL GEAR SOLID MASTER COLLECTION Vol 1 Official Gameplay and Platform Reveal Trailer
description: METAL GEAR SOLID: MASTER COLLECTION Vol. 1 launches October 24, 2023 for Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S, and Steam.

title: Super Mario Bros Wonder Official Announcement Trailer
description:
Super Mario Bros. Wonder is releasing for Nintendo Switch on October 20, 2023. A brand new 2D side scrolling Mario is coming out after nearly a decade! Check out the brand new trailer for Super Mario Bros. Wonder.


#SuperMarioBrosWonder #NintendoSwitch #gaming

title: DRAGON QUEST MONSTERS The Dark Prince Official Announcement Trailer
description:
DRAGON QUEST MONSTERS: The Dark Prince is coming to Nintendo Switch on December 1, 2023! 

DRAGON QUEST MONSTERS: The Dark Prince follows Psaro and his companion Rose as they travel through the demon realm of Nadiria. Explore and scout monsters onto your team, freely combine raised monsters to create more powerful allies, and take on enemies with your powerful team.

#dragonquest #monsters #gaming

title: Super Mario RPG Official Trailer
description:
Super Mario RPG is releasing for Nintendo Switch on November 17, 2023! 

Join Mario, Bowser, Peach, and original characters Mallow and Geno, in an RPG filled with twists and turns.

title: Detective Pikachu Returns Official Trailer
description: Solve mysteries with the personality-packed Detective Pikachu in Detective Pikachu Returns, coming to Nintendo Switch on October 6!
